    "This demo application supports Python debugging exercises and we plan to add support for C debugging exercises in the future.",
    "LimitationsNext, we discuss a few limitations of our study.",
    "Firstly, our classroom investigation was done using pre-selected exercises (instead of using real-time generation) to control the generation quality for the laboratory task.",
    "For future studies, it would be more informative to analyze students' performance on buggy exercises generated with LLMs in real-time.",
    "Secondly, we did not correlate students' success rates for debugging exercises with their long-term course performance."
